verse_part: Of those against whom I am not able
me, For I have been very
it. Oh, that You would bring
with them as You have dealt
visions; And they have not exposed
in derision at you; They hiss
And He has caused the enemy
me in so that I cannot
He is to me like a bear
Is it not from the mouth
for them Because of the destruction
It is we who have borne
at the risk of our lives
to us, for we have sinned
